This method is recommended over the baked in M365 app installer with Intune since the baked in method is treated as a LOB app and causes issues with ESP & Autopilot.

Generate your Config.xml at https://config.office.com/
  1. Make sure your config file is set to accept EULA & to not show install progress to end user.
  
Download the ODT executable at https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=49117
